*Zabava* je bila uspešna. (The party was successful.)
Mi smo se zabavljali. (We were having fun.)
Oni su provodili zabavu. (They were having a party.)
Ona je vodila *zabavu*. (She was leading the party.)
Pevač je popravio *zabavu*. (The singer livened up the party.)
Oni su uživali u zabavi. (They were enjoying the party.)
Ona je napravila *zabavu*. (She made a party.)
Mi smo napravili zabavu. (We made a party.)